data.description: Newly Built Salt Water Pool holds 27,000 Gallon of water with Quartz finish. Pool was completed in 2022. Garage is finished with Sheet rock Newly Remodeled in 2021. Flooring has been updated and new. Fireplace has also been remodeled to white stone. Home includes Paid Solar Panels and Security Cameras. Solar Panels are paid in full. There are two new front gates and curb appeal is very nice. Home is located in a great school district and great neighborhood. Property is very well maintained. Its a great investment or for a First time home Buyer. Home also comes with Safety Fence for the Pool. Seller will pay 7,500.00 Towards Closing Costs!
